== 6...h6 ==
Black pushes the bishop away, likely intending to go for either the [[/7. Bh4/7...b6|Tartakower]] or [[/7. Bh4/7...Ne4|Lasker's defence]].

Apart from White's main option '''[[/7. Bh4/]]''' they can also avoid these theoretical lines by playing '''[[/7. Bxf6/]]'''.

